="rich_pages wxw-img" data-aistatus="1" data-backh="325" data-backw="578" data-imgfileid="100156884" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width:100%; max-width: 600px" type="block" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/SKeDib1p4UA1icSZOH3UMyUgeFP7E6xibqnXxYstfn8SWQibianZTQWVhStkDh2iad0BUEXzIdEKJwHeD1ibyfyr8Ao17fibMD2Yic4u8Cz5gwxn3ps8/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></section><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span leaf="">近日，经过50余天施工，集装箱船“MSC科妮莉亚”号驶离广船国际所属文冲修造码头，扬帆起航。本次修理集多项节能环保升级于一体，工程规模大、技术标准高。项目团队高效完成轴带发电机加装、挡风墙增设、螺旋桨及导流罩换装等节能改造，同步开展舱盖、绑扎桥修理、舾装件换新，全船超水除锈涂装翻新及机舱主副机等设备全面大修，特检、改造、翻新同步推进，施工难度远超常规项目。</span></p><section data-role="outer" label="edit by 135editor" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="97392"><section style="margin:10px auto;"><section style="width:70px;margin:0px auto;box-sizing:border-box;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);"><section style="width:70px;box-sizing:border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.35802469135802467" data-w="81" style="width:100%; display:block; vertical-align:baseline; box-sizing:border-box; max-width: 600px" data-width="100%" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/7QRTvkK2qC7P1yl5iaQtEABnacY25BjbeKuMcRzXBO6VIQD6VxehqsdNh38icibSKdoviaWgygeWCVFTpnCiajqnIGg/640?wx_fmt=png"></section></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: center;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-aistatus="1" data-backh="237" data-backw="492" data-imgfileid="100156885" data-ratio="0.4817073170731707" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="492" style="width:100%; max-width: 600px" type="block" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/SKeDib1p4UA171lIAoic2Kozwk9YF7LU5Y48LNAhxAJ8oC1a5Tfl89w5iba8ic3wvRDOjD9wj0YOERTlwhSicxsFQ8dRBSG3u1XoqBsje2lrlRgU/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></section><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span leaf="">近日，七〇二所控股无锡东方船研高性能船艇工程有限公司承建的国内电池容量最大海上纯电客船“鹭江会客厅”下水。作为国内纯电船舶标杆作品，该船搭载大容量锂电池组，配备双电机与双全回转对转舵桨系统，并集成智能辅助航行系统，实现航行零排放、低噪音、无污染，全面践行绿色低碳发展方向。船舶采用多业态融合运营模式，灵活适配海上观光、商务会议、新品发布、特色餐饮、定制包船等多元场景，满足不同客群个性化需求。</span></p><section data-role="outer" label="edit by 135editor" data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="97392"><section style="margin:10px auto;"><section style="width:70px;margin:0px auto;box-sizing:border-box;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);"><section style="width:70px;box-sizing:border-box;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.35802469135802467" data-w="81" style="width:100%; display:block; vertical-align:baseline; box-sizing:border-box; max-width: 600px" data-width="100%" data-aistatus="1" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/7QRTvkK2qC7P1yl5iaQtEABnacY25BjbeKuMcRzXBO6VIQD6VxehqsdNh38icibSKdoviaWgygeWCVFTpnCiajqnIGg/640?wx_fmt=png"></section></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: center;" nodeleaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-aistatus="1" data-backh="312" data-backw="554" data-imgfileid="100156886" data-ratio="0.5631768953068592" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width:100%; max-width: 600px" type="block" src="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/SKeDib1p4UA3Rich3LWfUbAza54dLgrIPhX6YcZ8HYORlU00DkDCMZhibMUFBrmHxugibKWxXk6dBIJ3ru2OnXIknu7qJK208xNtrFBicdg8TYxc/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></section><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span leaf="">3月27日，六〇五院为广州公交集团客轮有限公司打造的 “不夜侯” 号纯电动客船交付。作为珠江夜游重点新能源项目，“不夜侯”号纯电动客船是六〇五院继“状元舫”号后，打造的又一精品纯电客船。该船以绿色、智能、文化为核心理念打造，搭载全回转纯电力推进系统，兼具低能耗、低噪音、零排放优势，精准契合绿色发展需求。</span></p><section data-pm-slice="0 0 []" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 10